title: Modaris 6 Diamino 5 +Licenses +Key Fashion Cad
description:
Hello There.

This is the CAD software from Lectra for the professional fashion bussness.

It includes:
    *Diamino V6R1
    *Modaris V5R3
    *MarkerCreation V5R3
    *VigiPrint V2.4c4
    *ButtonboxV1.1c4 
    *Xchangcut V5R3.
    *Plus license files & Hardware Key.
	
   All working till 2027.

Requeriments:
   CPU: A regular machine
   OS:  WinXP / Win7 32bit	
	
 In the installation process it wil ask for a key to run, then you should contact me to get one. For Bussness purposes I think it was better to keep it away to the crowd.

 Even after installation is done the software wont run because it needs a License and a Key. As this is a a Professional software I can offer the license and key for a fair price. This full package from original supplier would cost about U$22.000! I do it below 1K! This realease does work great. Have instaled and used it for a good time.
